Name: Qwilfish Bow
LongDescription: Makes thrown or hurled items bounce off the Pokémon. Keep it in the Treasure Bag to give its benefit to all of these team members: Qwilfish.  Finding a Qwilfish Bow at the Croagunk Swap Shop is very lucky! Make sure you get it before someone else does! An item with a ☆☆☆-rarity rating is very hard to get. It's beyond valuable!
